    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc210539n520as39347043658742">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Four diaries kept by Perry; 1 address book; a scrapbook; and 3 photographs of Perry by George C. Cox.</p>
    </scopecontent>
